title: 84. Esthetician Mistakes + What We Can Learn From Them.
description:
In this episode, I want to share about some mistakes I've made myself, and some I have noticed within the industry. No one is perfect, and no one should suffer and feel alone when things happen. Let me know which ones resonate with you on social media. ☺️
